<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.2">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2024-03-30T16:20:52+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Hermosawave Photography</title><subtitle>A series of daily landscape photographs by Daniel Sofer, 20 years running.</subtitle><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><entry><title type="html">Jojakkoji Temple・常寂光寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240330/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Jojakkoji Temple・常寂光寺" /><published>2024-03-30T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-03-30T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/jojakkoji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240330/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
After a long interval of cold, rainy weather, a few days of warm sunshine and... poof! Now the cherry blossoms are coming out everywhere in Kyoto. This is at Jojakkoji temple in Arashiyama.
</p>
<p class="jp">
長い間、冷たい雨が降り続いた後、暖かい日差しが数日続き、そして...パッ！今、京都のあちこちで桜が咲いています。これは嵐山の常寂光寺。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Sakura" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[After a long interval of cold, rainy weather, a few days of warm sunshine and... poof! Now the cherry blossoms are coming out everywhere in Kyoto. This is at Jojakkoji temple in Arashiyama. 長い間、冷たい雨が降り続いた後、暖かい日差しが数日続き、そして...パッ！今、京都のあちこちで桜が咲いています。これは嵐山の常寂光寺。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08520-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08520-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kurumazaki Jinja・車折神社</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240329/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kurumazaki Jinja・車折神社" /><published>2024-03-29T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-03-29T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kurumazaki-jinja</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240329/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Warm spring day brings out visitors to Kurmazaki Jinja, both human and otherwise.
</p>
<p class="jp">
暖かな春の日、車折神社を訪れる人たち。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Sakura" /><category term="Shrines" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Warm spring day brings out visitors to Kurmazaki Jinja, both human and otherwise. 暖かな春の日、車折神社を訪れる人たち。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_DSCF9552-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_DSCF9552-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Weeping Cherry・枝垂れ桜</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240327/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Weeping Cherry・枝垂れ桜" /><published>2024-03-27T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-03-27T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/shidarezakura</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240327/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The famous weeping cherry tree at the Kyoto Gyoen Garden is in bloom now, and many visitors braved the mud to take photos.
</p>
<p class="jp">
京都御苑の有名な枝垂れ桜が開花。多くの観光客が泥の中を歩いて写真を撮っていました。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Sakura" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The famous weeping cherry tree at the Kyoto Gyoen Garden is in bloom now, and many visitors braved the mud to take photos. 京都御苑の有名な枝垂れ桜が開花。多くの観光客が泥の中を歩いて写真を撮っていました。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08417-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08417-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Watery Tree・木から水滴</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240324/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Watery Tree・木から水滴" /><published>2024-03-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-03-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/momiji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240324/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Water drops hang from a tree getting ready to unfurl its leaves. A boat goes by on the Oigawa River.
</p>
<p class="jp">
葉を広げようとしている木から滴り落ちる水。大堰川を行き交うボート。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Boats" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Water drops hang from a tree getting ready to unfurl its leaves. A boat goes by on the Oigawa River. 葉を広げようとしている木から滴り落ちる水。大堰川を行き交うボート。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08333.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08333.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Azaleas at the Bamboo Grove・竹林のつつじ</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240323/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Azaleas at the Bamboo Grove・竹林のつつじ" /><published>2024-03-23T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-03-23T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/azalea</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240323/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Beautiful azalea tree blooming at the entrance to the bamboo grove, on a rainy day.
</p>
<p class="jp">
雨の日、竹林の入り口に咲く美しいつつじ。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Beautiful azalea tree blooming at the entrance to the bamboo grove, on a rainy day. 雨の日、竹林の入り口に咲く美しいつつじ。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08362-2-bright.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08362-2-bright.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Twilight Train・トワイライト・トレイン</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240322/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Twilight Train・トワイライト・トレイン" /><published>2024-03-22T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-03-22T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/randen</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240322/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Kyoto's Randen line train rolls into the station.
</p>
<p class="jp">
駅に到着した京都の嵐電。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Trains" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Kyoto's Randen line train rolls into the station. 駅に到着した京都の嵐電。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_IMG_9406.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_IMG_9406.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Spring Snow・春雪</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240321/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Spring Snow・春雪" /><published>2024-03-21T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-03-21T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/snow</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240321/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A light dusting of overnight snow on one of the kawazu zakara cherry trees that have bloomed in Arashiyama.
</p>
<p class="jp">
嵐山の河津桜に一夜にして小雪。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Snow" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A light dusting of overnight snow on one of the kawazu zakara cherry trees that have bloomed in Arashiyama. 嵐山の河津桜に一夜にして小雪。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08316.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08316.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sakura Season・桜の季節</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240319/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sakura Season・桜の季節" /><published>2024-03-19T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-03-19T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sakura</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240319/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Back in Kyoto where the early cherry blossoms are in full bloom, but most trees have not yet started.
</p>
<p class="jp">
早咲きの桜が満開の京都では、まだほとんどの木が咲き始めていません。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Back in Kyoto where the early cherry blossoms are in full bloom, but most trees have not yet started. 早咲きの桜が満開の京都では、まだほとんどの木が咲き始めていません。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08286-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2403_A7R08286-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Tokyo Tower Skyline</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240318/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Tokyo Tower Skyline" /><published>2024-03-18T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-03-18T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tokyotower</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240318/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
